radio_info.short: EvoSonic radio - the legendary electronic music dj radio started broadcasting on May 1st 1997 from Cologne, Germany via Astra satellite and German cable network.
radio_info.rest: It specialized in presenting the full range of electronic music with djs from all over europe. With its unique concept evosonic radio was ahead of the times and soon gathered tens of thousands of fans and listeners all over Europe, most of them in Germany. The broadcast was shut down on October 1st 1999 - but its spirit outlasted.
